Bayesian Inference



Files
	BayesianNetworkRG
		-contians information for bayesian networks
	RandomVariableRG
		-class for random variables
	BNOde
		-wrapper class for RandomVariableRG
	CPTRG
		-cpt table for a randomVariableRG
	exactInferenceRG
		-formulae for the enumeration-ask algorithm
	Gibbs-sampling/rejectionSampling/LikelihoodWeighting
		-gibbs sampling/rejectionSampling/likelihood-weighting algorithm
	InferenceRG
		-parent class for all inference algorithms
	xmlBIFParser
		-contains code for parsing XMLBIF files
	
Runnign instructions
any of the inference classes will run the program

command- "java [program] Query E1=e1,E2=e2...En=en"


where
	Query- query variable
	E1...En = evidence variable (for givens)
	e1...1n = the value of the corresponding evidence variables

example- "java RejectionSampling B J=true,M=false"
	queries RejectionSamlping for proobabilities of variable B given J=true and M=false